{"tid":1373144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術分享]相傳岳飛用斬馬腳大破金兵","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:45.000Z","uid":68347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e788bddf6c0d52ace2d98c0ce71a969b5d238b6","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"前線面對一波推進緊金兵, 或者己方進攻既時候<br />\n<br />\n不如考慮下用長遮柄(或其他有勾物件) 去勾腳<br />\n<br />\n勾跌一個就有人落單<br />\n<br />\n敵方為左救起隊友只會停止推進, 如無視則會人踩人<br />\n<br />\n效果有二:<br />\n一. 防守時,打散敵人衝擊<br />\n<br />\n二. 進攻時,可逐個擊破<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/27/EApe87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F27%2FEApe87.png&h=1e3a6299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有手足能夠勾到一兩個,必有強大效果"},{"pid":"be33111eca4ea18aa0dadacb305d45811e899961","tid":1373144,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d7b9a15cb8437ffb90c07196bbb8ac663c00435d","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cf40cf9eb257ea5d2e6a47b96e750a202113eb8","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"俾意見"},{"pid":"de68b763b03abd17fbe5fb92335541e2fcecd195","tid":1373144,"uid":219444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"953da7b8353b5a2d0daa91c4ac84b0d5a47be7d3","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"340b75b34da9ceffe0a25e70d7ed323922ccb9d8","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1591554f0fcbf293d86067ed06925a8471a39575","tid":1373144,"uid":68347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:56:5